for the rise of Xiangjiang.

109
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:07,760
Runzhi.

110
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:09,280
The solidarity rally for Mr. Chen Duxiu

111
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,000
is about to leave.

112
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,520
Runzhi. Runzhi.

113
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,800
Have all the inaugural issues of the "Xiangjiang Review"

114
00:06:11,796 --> 00:06:13,514
[Peng Huan, styled Yinbai, Member of the Xinmin Society]

115
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:13,840
come out?

116
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:16,240
It's all here.

117
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:23,440
Runzhi.

118
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,440
Well done.

119
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:31,280
These ten days,

120
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,480
one person writing,

121
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:33,920
one person editing,

122
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,200
one person typesetting,

123
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,560
one person printing,

124
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:38,720
to finish the inaugural issue.

125
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:39,760
It's not easy.

126
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:45,760
Here. Eat something.

127
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:47,120
Here.

128
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:49,840
What is this?

129
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,280
Mr. Zhongfu,

130
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,960
like a moth to a flame,

131
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,640
would rather go to jail

132
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:56,160
and wake the world up.

133
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,400
What is it

134
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,400
when I wait for young people to suffer?

135
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:08,560
You've printed six of them since you came up here.

136
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:09,920
Well written.

137
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:14,240
What is the biggest problem in the world?

138
00:07:11,710 --> 00:07:13,788
[He Shuheng, styled Yuheng, Member of the Xinmin Society]

139
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:16,400
Eating is the biggest problem.

140
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,480
What is the strongest power?

141
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:20,720
The strength of the people is the strongest.

142
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:22,160
What must not be feared?

143
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,760
Do not fear Heaven.

144
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:25,600
Do not fear ghosts.

145
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:27,360
Do not fear the dead.

146
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,360
Do not fear bureaucrats.

147
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:31,200
Do not fear warlords.

148
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:33,760
Do not fear capitalists!

149
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:35,120
Beautiful!

150
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,000
Delightful!

151
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,280
It's all finished.

152
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,000
Hurry up.

153
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:42,080
Send this inaugural issue to each school

154
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:43,520
and then distribute the presentations.

155
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:44,880
Very well.

156
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:46,160
Hurrah!

157
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,720
Fellow citizens,

158
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:54,240
Everyone knows

159
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:58,080
Mr. Chen Duxiu is a star in Chinese ideological circles.

160
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:01,120
His knowledge of China is always profound.

161
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:02,720
China now

162
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:04,800
is in extreme danger.

163
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,120
In 1919,

164
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,760
young Mao Zedong spent a summer

165
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:12,320
like fire in Changsha.

166
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:14,400
He is the editor-in-chief and lead writer

167
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,760
of the "Xiangjiang Review",

168
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,520
and directed the Hunan Federation of Students

169
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,600
to launch the Hunan Federation of Societies

170
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:21,760
to organize a 10-member group to save the nation,

171
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:24,800
to give a speech in the streets of the society,

172
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,720
and to widely mobilize the people

173
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:30,000
to set off the whole society to rescue Chen Duxiu.

174
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:31,440
He pointed out

175
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:35,680
that Mr. Chen Duxiu is a star in Chinese ideological circles,

176
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,440
and because of science and democracy

177
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:38,880
he offended the reactionary authorities.

178
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:42,720
His arrest will not only not harm him

179
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:45,040
but will leave a great legacy

180
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:47,360
that will make the new ideas he advocated

181
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:50,240
more glorious and far-reaching.

182
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,760
Our Tianjin Student Union Newspaper

183
00:08:55,037 --> 00:09:04,163
[Tianjin]

184
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:56,960
After the publication of the inaugural issue,

185
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,720
it has received a lot of attention from all walks of life.

186
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:00,640
Many readers have written to us

187
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:01,600
or visited us

188
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:02,560
to ask to hear from us

189
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:04,080
more news from Mr. Chen Duxiu of Peking University.

190
00:09:04,562 --> 00:09:07,041
[Zhou Enlai, styled Xiangyu, editor-in-chief of the "Tianjin Student Union Newspaper"]

191
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,840
I hope we can publish more

192
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,960
articles on this subject.

193
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:09,200
So rescuing Mr. Chen Duxiu

194
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:11,120
will be the focus of our next issue.

195
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:12,480
Everyone needs to work hard

196
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:14,560
to organize more important articles.

197
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,000
Please.

198
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:20,640
Let's split up.

199
00:09:22,069 --> 00:09:26,283
[Beijing Metropolitan Police Department]

200
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:44,880
Professor Chen, bright under the high light.

201
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:49,040
This one is too small. It hurts my eyes.

202
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:53,840
Director Wu, you should call me number 178.

203
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:58,560
Professor Chen is very observant of prison rules.

204
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:03,280
Number 178 is what I call you in public.

205
00:10:03,483 --> 00:10:06,280
[Chen Duxiu, styled Zhongfu, Professor at Peking University]

206
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:04,400
Today,

207
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:06,880
I'm visiting as a fellow villager.

208
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:10,800
Of course, I have to call you Professor Chen.

209
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,840
How are you, Professor Chen?

210
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,200
Let's have a chat.

211
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:23,760
Your place, your call.

212
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:27,360
Professor Chen is also happy.

213
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:31,200
I had my guys

214
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,120
scrounge this up.

215
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:35,200
After you have gone to jail,

216
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:37,200
you can stay and read some of the reports.

217
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:39,600
Thanks a lot.

218
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,440
Thank you, Director Wu.

219
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:46,880
It's me who should say thank you.

220
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:49,600
How do you say this?

221
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:52,240
You'll understand it when you read the newspaper.

222
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:56,480
Professor Chen, it is because of you.

223
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,760
I, Wu Bingxiang,

224
00:10:58,320 --> 00:11:00,960
have suddenly become a newspaper sensation.

225
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:06,000
There are only two news figures in the newspaper now.

226
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:09,440
Chen Duxiu is a star-studded man.

227
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:12,320
I, Wu Bingxiang, have been criticized.

228
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:17,440
That's what you deserve.

229
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:19,200
Blame no one else.

230
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:22,400
There are also brave words.

231
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,160
You talk about this "declaration".

232
00:11:24,560 --> 00:11:25,600
Let me read it to you.

233
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:31,680
Fortunately, police chief Wu Bingxiang

234
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:34,000
has a novel brain.

235
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:35,680
Although threatened by all sides

236
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:38,240
and secretly encouraged by the traditionalists,

237
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:42,880
he has never treated Chen harshly.

238
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:45,440
That's true.

239
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:49,120
It said Wu Bingxiang didn't treat you badly.

240
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:53,040
It's not true to say that the traditionalists are secretly encouraging me.

241
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:56,640
Look here, there are some.

242
00:11:58,560 --> 00:12:02,560
Ma Jichang, the leader of Tongcheng School, and Yao Yong

243
00:12:03,040 --> 00:12:05,680
issued a statement urging the Metropolitan Police Department

244
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:09,760
to unconditionally release Chen Duxiu.

245
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:16,240
This is very touching to me.

246
00:12:17,040 --> 00:12:18,320
Whether the people are for or against,

247
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:19,440
Director Wu,

248
00:12:19,760 --> 00:12:21,360
I really want to thank you for bringing me in.

249
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:23,360
Professor Chen,

250
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,680
you don't have to get carried away.

251
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:28,880
Don't forget Cai Yuanpei's sentence.

252
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:31,920
The story of the roadside children who kill the king's horse.

253
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,600
Beware of being killed.

254
00:12:35,280 --> 00:12:36,880
I, Chen, know myself.

255
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:44,720
This is the inaugural issue of the "Xiangjiang Review".

256
00:12:46,800 --> 00:12:48,400
This Zedong guy?

257
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:51,360
Not only did he make you a star in the ideological circle,

258
00:12:51,920 --> 00:12:53,040
he even shouted:

259
00:12:53,280 --> 00:12:57,440
long live Mr. Chen's supreme spirit!

260
00:12:58,720 --> 00:13:00,000
This is too much, isn't it?

261
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:02,720
Director Wu,

262
00:13:03,680 --> 00:13:05,680
maybe it's someone like Zedong

263
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:09,600
who will one day destroy your old world.

264
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:15,280
Can you destroy the old world?

265
00:13:16,160 --> 00:13:18,560
It is too early to tell.

266
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:21,120
I want to tell Professor Chen,

267
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,520
because of your imprisonment,

268
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:26,720
it really brought great trouble to the government.

269
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:30,400
Now almost the whole of China is moving.

270
00:13:30,640 --> 00:13:32,560
It is unprecedented.

271
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:34,000
It's an unexpected thing?

272
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:37,440
But this is not a good thing for Professor Chen.

273
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:42,320
Now everyone knows,

274
00:13:42,800 --> 00:13:44,640
you are the number one political enemy of the government.

275
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:48,800
Many people are yelling at me to hand you over.

276
00:13:49,280 --> 00:13:51,040
Once you get out of the police station,

277
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:54,080
you can imagine the consequences.

278
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,960
It's nothing more than a broken head.

